removePattern

public void removePattern(TreeParent node)
In reverse DFS traversal order, remove all children of a pattern Base Case 1: Node is null, return Base Case 2: Node is a leaf, remove the node from the parent Recursion: For each node not a leaf, recursively call this function, and after all functions removes all descendants of this node, remove the node from its parent.
